#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "thig3.1:3.1"
msgid "1. Aparāsāmātherīgāthā"
msgstr ""

#. </h1></div><blockquote class="gatha"><p><a class="sc" id="1"></a><a
#. class="verse-num-sc" id="verse-num-sc39"></a><a class="verse-num-pts"
#. id="verse-num-pts39"></a>
msgctxt "thig3.1:4.1"
msgid "“Paṇṇavīsativassāni,"
msgstr "Twenty five years have passed"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thig3.1:4.2"
msgid "yato pabbajitāya me;"
msgstr "Since I became one gone forth"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thig3.1:4.3"
msgid "Nābhijānāmi cittassa,"
msgstr "I'm not aware of having gained"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thig3.1:4.4"
msgid "samaṃ laddhaṃ kudācanaṃ."
msgstr "Peace of mind at any time"

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="2"></a><a class="verse-num-sc"
#. id="verse-num-sc40"></a><a class="verse-num-pts" id="verse-num-pts40"></a>
msgctxt "thig3.1:5.1"
msgid "Aladdhā cetaso santiṃ,"
msgstr "Without gaining peace of mind"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thig3.1:5.2"
msgid "citte avasavattinī;"
msgstr "Without mastery over the mind"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thig3.1:5.3"
msgid "Tato saṃvegamāpādiṃ,"
msgstr "I experienced a sense of urgency"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thig3.1:5.4"
msgid "saritvā jinasāsanaṃ."
msgstr "Having remembered the conqueror's teaching"

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="3"></a><a class="verse-num-sc"
#. id="verse-num-sc41"></a><a class="verse-num-pts" id="verse-num-pts41"></a><a
#. class="pts" id="pts128"></a>
msgctxt "thig3.1:6.1"
msgid "Bahūhi dukkhadhammehi,"
msgstr "Delighting in heedfulness"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thig3.1:6.2"
msgid "appamādaratāya me;"
msgstr "Due to much suffering of phenomena"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thig3.1:6.3"
msgid "Taṇhakkhayo anuppatto,"
msgstr "Having realised the end of craving"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thig3.1:6.4"
msgid "kataṃ buddhassa sāsanaṃ;"
msgstr "I've done what Buddha taught"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thig3.1:6.5"
msgid "Ajja me sattamī ratti,"
msgstr "This is the seventh day and night"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thig3.1:6.6"
msgid "yato taṇhā visositā”ti."
msgstr "Since my craving dried up"

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsutta"><a class="sc" id="4"></a>
